-- Lew Urges Congress to Raise Debt Limit to Give Economy Certainty
-- B y   I a n   K a t z
-- 2013-08-27T11:48:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-27/lew-urges-congress-to-raise-debt-limit-to-give-economy-certainty.html
U.S. Treasury Secretary Jacob J. Lew
said Congress needs to raise the nation’s debt ceiling to help
give the economy some “certainty.”  “Congress has to act,” Lew said in an interview today on
CNBC television. “We are not going to be negotiating over the
debt limit.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
